data.description: HOLIDAY SEASON REDUCTION !!- Meticulously maintained by ORIGINAL OWNER. Won't Last Long given its price, amenities, and location in Alden Bridge. Yard has full sprinkler system, high ceilings, tile flooring in kitchen and breakfast area, Foyer, and Bath Floors. Patio with access from family room, rear yard fully fenced. Owners says the greatest attribute is the location, along with the high elevated lot, and quiet cul-de-sac street. What can I ay...IMMACULATE IS THE WORD.
